"2 teaspoons canola oil","2/3 cup chopped onion","1 1/2 tablespoons chili powder","2 teaspoons garlic powder","1 1/2 teaspoons ground cumin","1/2 teaspoon dried oregano","1 pound 93% lean ground sirloin","1/2 cup unsalted chicken stock (such as Swanson)","1/2 teaspoon kosher salt","8  corn tostadas","1 1/2 cups shredded romaine lettuce","1 cup chopped seeded tomato","1/4 cup light sour cream","1  (8.5-ounce) pouch precooked brown rice (such as Uncle Ben's)","1/4 cup chopped fresh cilantro","1 tablespoon lime juice"